title: Seigrid☆Darkness
original_name: せいぐりっど ☆ だーくねす
sinopse:
Yuki is invited to be a test player in the MMORPG his aunt is making. As he enters the RPG world, he meets a beautiful, half-naked girl, who is being attacked by a slime. Is this the start of something?

(Source: Fujimi Shobo, translated)
